{"tid":1361630,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］新方向或合體運動","createTime":"2019-07-24T15:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T16:00:58.000Z","uid":263927,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6f6dad3825f0cff696a39d2d3a03d7d85142a530","tid":1361630,"uid":263927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:53:50.000Z","msg":"其實6月已經攪過MTR不合作運動<br />\n效果如何，大家有目共睹<br />\n<br />\n所以小弟有個小建議，可以結合過去成功經驗再下一城！<br />\n例如<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連儂列車/連儂車廂</span></span><br />\n或者仲可以有更好既方法，路唔只一條<br />\n但一定要團結！"},{"pid":"e7e53e4ecab787a8e1139b058cfb1bd4af0365c4","tid":1361630,"uid":287844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:54:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">時間無多，<br />\n幫手推翻<strong>機場集會行動post</strong>上熱門，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n幫手推行動post<br />\n熱門一個都冇</span></span></span></strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">機場就係重要嘅命脈，<br />\n發揮和理非最大影響力，<br />\n到時就有bargaining power!!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n遍地開花，可以向外國旅客宣揚香港嘅運動。派多國語言嘅宣傳, 播大電視。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">星星之火可燎原<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n但如果引發到罷工<br />\n少人上貨同行李<br />\n空運減慢&amp;nbsp;<br />\n減怛機倉清理&amp;nbsp;<br />\n冇人維修飛機&amp;nbsp;<br />\n唔夠人手指揮航空交通，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">泊位費成本每秒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n所帶來既嘅<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">係世界性影響<br />\n</span></span><br />\n到時各國都要理<br />\n係衝擊所達唔到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">對準弱點 發揮和理非最強影響力</span></span><br />\n￼￼￼￼￼<br />\n<br />\n一齊入機場嘆冷氣[/orange][/size=5]<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Link:&amp;nbsp;</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354831\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354831</a>"},{"pid":"852a1e3dad4ca28d5f9a31a71b812f17c18bf468","tid":1361630,"uid":263927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:54:33.000Z","msg":"參考下<br />\n集思廣益"},{"pid":"5fd285bb5f9979caeff4dece57f11821105f7946","tid":1361630,"uid":263927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:54:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3f047587e76245a33628f1629990d3970d06d54","tid":1361630,"uid":263927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:54:55.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"578f443f56cb8a58e4ecae973a961bdec07c4f37","tid":1361630,"uid":263927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:55:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ebc65e2c1992527b7436971d063bd4b26784856a","tid":1361630,"uid":263927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:55:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5daa48e63369ea0b775b4183c4748844a2fbe330","tid":1361630,"uid":263927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:55:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"584bddea40f39ab352e49ede848eb6d987ac7012","tid":1361630,"uid":263927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:55:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6dc562de908934ab9d74d05e3066912f69915f3f","tid":1361630,"uid":263927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201